    • Constructor Detail

      • MotionProfileController

        public MotionProfileController(double kp,
                               double ki,
                               double kd,
                               double kffv,
                               double kffa,
                               double tolerance)
        Generates a simple motion profile controller
        Parameters:
        kp - The proportional feedback constant.
        ki - The integral feedback constant.
        kd - The derivative feedback constant.
        kffv - The velocity feed forward constant. Typically 1 / max velocity.
        kffa - The acceleration feed forward constant.
        tolerance - The absolute tolerance.

      • MotionProfileController

        public MotionProfileController(double kp,
                               double ki,
                               double kd,
                               double kffv,
                               double kffa,
                               double tolerance,
                               Clock clock)
        Generates a simple motion profile controller
        Parameters:
        kp - The proportional feedback constant.
        ki - The integral feedback constant.
        kd - The derivative feedback constant.
        kffv - The velocity feed forward constant. Typically 1 / max velocity.
        kffa - The acceleration feed forward constant.
        tolerance - The absolute tolerance.
        clock - The clock to use.
